00:00:11,290 --> 00:00:20,880


2
00:00:36,010 --> 00:00:41,680
♫  No matter if it's a rainy day or a sunny day  ♫

3
00:00:41,680 --> 00:00:47,120
♫  As long as you are by my side  ♫ 
 ♫  Even the sunlight becomes dazzling  ♫

4
00:00:47,120 --> 00:00:52,830
♫  Thinking too much, blindly guessing  ♫ 
 ♫  Why not find a day to meet  ♫

5
00:00:52,830 --> 00:00:59,260
♫  Saying too much, there's no "what if"  ♫ 
 ♫  Might as well go on an adventure  ♫

6
00:00:59,260 --> 00:01:02,780
♫  I stand in the shadows  ♫

7
00:01:02,780 --> 00:01:08,120
♫  Reaching out, waiting for your rescue  ♫

8
00:01:08,120 --> 00:01:13,070
♫  Between you and me  ♫ 
 ♫  Even if the world collapses  ♫

9
00:01:13,070 --> 00:01:17,160
♫  No matter how far the distance  ♫

10
00:01:17,160 --> 00:01:21,620
♫  Nothing can stop our meeting  ♫

11
00:01:21,620 --> 00:01:28,610
♫  Stepping through the long dark night  ♫ 
 ♫  You are standing at the finish line  ♫

12
00:01:28,610 --> 00:01:32,820
♫  Protecting you is my tiny wish  ♫

13
00:01:32,820 --> 00:01:37,170
♫  Goodbye to the shy me of the past  ♫

14
00:01:37,170 --> 00:01:42,530
♫  Because of you, I have become a little braver  ♫

15
00:01:42,530 --> 00:01:46,250
   

16
00:01:46,250 --> 00:01:49,280
   
   

17
00:02:01,670 --> 00:02:03,340
We're here.

18
00:02:03,340 --> 00:02:05,520
Go home first. I'll make sure you get in.

19
00:02:05,520 --> 00:02:07,450
I want to see you go up first.

20
00:02:07,450 --> 00:02:08,780
You go first. I'll watch you.

21
00:02:08,780 --> 00:02:10,720
- You go upstairs first. 
 - You first.

22
00:02:10,720 --> 00:02:11,890
Hurry up.

23
00:02:11,890 --> 00:02:14,520
- Hurry up. 
 - Give me a hug then.

24
00:02:14,520 --> 00:02:16,260
Hug me.

25
00:02:23,060 --> 00:02:24,370
Just let me hold you a little longer.

26
00:02:24,370 --> 00:02:26,270
Aunt Lin.

27
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:28,710
You've been training well, Jing Xi Chi.

28
00:02:28,710 --> 00:02:31,110
Compete with me some other day.

29
00:02:32,340 --> 00:02:33,940
You're back.

30
00:02:34,512 --> 00:02:36,808
- Did you come back together? 
 - Yeah.

31
00:02:39,060 --> 00:02:41,430
Mom, why are you here?

32
00:02:41,430 --> 00:02:45,660
I just went to Aunt Hao's place.

33
00:02:46,308 --> 00:02:48,340
Aunt Hao's place...

34
00:02:48,340 --> 00:02:49,840
Aunt, I'll head home now.

35
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:52,510
- Bye. 
 - Bye.

36
00:02:53,780 --> 00:02:56,475
Let's go, Mom.

37
00:03:24,220 --> 00:03:27,310
- Men should be responsible. 
 - What?

38
00:03:31,100 --> 00:03:33,430
I already figured it out.

39
00:03:33,430 --> 00:03:38,820
Back in high school, you were already circling around Huan Er.

40
00:03:40,190 --> 00:03:42,850
- Did I? 
 - You didn't?

41
00:03:44,750 --> 00:03:48,300
I think I did.

42
00:03:53,430 --> 00:03:58,020
Since you're together now, be good to Huan Er. Got it?

43
00:04:01,430 --> 00:04:03,540
You've really grown up.

44
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:06,475
I'm going to bed.

45
00:04:50,540 --> 00:04:57,530
 If I told you that I turned into someone I don't even like... 

46
00:04:58,370 --> 00:05:03,250
 would you still want to be with me? 

47
00:05:26,840 --> 00:05:28,610
Hello? Mom.

48
00:05:31,400 --> 00:05:35,200
I've decided to study abroad.

49
00:05:54,730 --> 00:05:57,860
 Can we talk after your exam? 

50
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:29,772
Why isn't your mom home today?

51
00:06:29,772 --> 00:06:31,880
She had to go to the hospital.

52
00:06:31,880 --> 00:06:34,440
Did your parents ask you anything when you left?

53
00:06:34,440 --> 00:06:36,880
They went out too.

54
00:06:36,880 --> 00:06:43,070
Speaking of, I think they love each other more than before after my mom got sick.

55
00:06:43,070 --> 00:06:47,600
Why aren't they home when we came to visit for the holidays?

56
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:49,980
But I can understand your dad.

57
00:06:49,980 --> 00:06:52,980
Aunt Li Na just recovered from a serious illness.

58
00:06:52,980 --> 00:06:56,100
Your dad must be cherishing his time with her.

59
00:06:56,100 --> 00:06:58,180
Let's not disturb their alone time.

60
00:06:58,180 --> 00:07:00,320
Got it.

61
00:07:01,180 --> 00:07:02,780
I'm getting old now.

62
00:07:02,780 --> 00:07:05,270
I forgot to take my phone when I went out.

63
00:07:09,180 --> 00:07:11,780
Huan Er didn't close the window.

64
00:07:11,780 --> 00:07:17,170
Well, I wish we could be like them when we're old.

65
00:07:18,540 --> 00:07:20,500
Of course.

66
00:07:20,500 --> 00:07:25,510
Then... will you remember the first time we held hands,

67
00:07:25,510 --> 00:07:29,440
our first kiss, and the first time you confessed?

68
00:07:30,510 --> 00:07:32,660
Not necessarily.

69
00:07:32,660 --> 00:07:34,586
Jing Xi Chi, what do you mean?

70
00:07:34,586 --> 00:07:37,120
If you don't remember now, later...

71
00:07:43,100 --> 00:07:45,420
Chen Huan Er, what are you doing?

72
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:48,730
Dad!

73
00:07:50,540 --> 00:07:51,860
Explain!

74
00:07:51,860 --> 00:07:52,950
When did this start?

75
00:07:52,950 --> 00:07:54,920
- A few days ago. 
 - I wasn't asking you.

76
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:56,830
I was asking him. When did this start?

77
00:07:56,830 --> 00:07:59,470
All right, you're scaring them.

78
00:07:59,470 --> 00:08:01,270
Tell me.

79
00:08:03,050 --> 00:08:04,540
Aunt Li Na.

80
00:08:04,540 --> 00:08:06,200
Uncle Chen.

81
00:08:06,810 --> 00:08:10,730
Huan Er and I started dating officially two days ago.

82
00:08:10,730 --> 00:08:12,470
Come on, Jing Xi Chi.

83
00:08:12,470 --> 00:08:14,431
I asked you to take care of her.

84
00:08:14,431 --> 00:08:16,330
You two... Is this how you take care of her?

85
00:08:16,330 --> 00:08:18,340
- Calm down. 
 - Dad.

86
00:08:18,340 --> 00:08:19,830
Sorry, Uncle Chen.

87
00:08:19,830 --> 00:08:25,170
I didn't say anything before because I didn't know how to bring it up.

88
00:08:26,510 --> 00:08:28,910
I really like Huan Er.

89
00:08:28,910 --> 00:08:32,420
I promise to take good care of her.

90
00:08:32,420 --> 00:08:34,200
Don't feed me that crap.

91
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:36,053
I'm telling you. I've gone through this before.

92
00:08:36,053 --> 00:08:39,030
When you're young, who doesn't say one thing and do another while dating?

93
00:08:39,030 --> 00:08:40,510
Why didn't you tell me in person?

94
00:08:40,510 --> 00:08:41,808
Why hide it?

95
00:08:41,808 --> 00:08:43,660
You're just a little liar. You know that?

96
00:08:43,660 --> 00:08:45,630
- Uncle Chen, please listen— 
 - Don't explain to me.

97
00:08:45,630 --> 00:08:47,870
Why explain to me? I don't want to hear it.

98
00:08:47,870 --> 00:08:50,110
Go on home. I'll handle my dad.

99
00:08:50,110 --> 00:08:52,060
Just go for now. It's all right.

100
00:08:52,060 --> 00:08:53,780
Uncle Chen.

101
00:08:53,780 --> 00:08:55,300
I'll go home now.

102
00:08:55,300 --> 00:08:57,150
I'll come see you once you've cooled off.

103
00:08:57,150 --> 00:08:59,475
What? Don't come to me. I'll deal with your mom.

104
00:08:59,475 --> 00:09:02,420
- How dare you come to me? 
 - What the hell are you doing?

105
00:09:02,420 --> 00:09:03,630
Xi Chi is a good kid.

106
00:09:03,630 --> 00:09:05,750
Oh please. What's so great about him? He's just a little liar.

107
00:09:05,750 --> 00:09:07,390
Enough.

108
00:09:07,390 --> 00:09:09,150
Why are you so agitated?

109
00:09:09,150 --> 00:09:10,080
Dad!

110
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:11,840
Why are you so angry?

111
00:09:11,840 --> 00:09:14,390
I just have a boyfriend.

112
00:09:14,390 --> 00:09:17,275
I didn't dare to tell you because I was afraid you'd behave like this.

113
00:09:17,275 --> 00:09:19,264
What? Are you saying that I'm wrong?

114
00:09:19,264 --> 00:09:21,831
- He stole you! How could I not be angry? 
 - He didn't steal me!

115
00:09:21,831 --> 00:09:23,630
What do you mean he didn't steal you?

116
00:09:23,630 --> 00:09:25,230
How did he steal your daughter?

117
00:09:25,230 --> 00:09:26,986
Xi Chi is a good kid.

118
00:09:26,986 --> 00:09:30,200
When I was hospitalized some time ago, he's been helping out. Didn't you see him?

119
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:31,700
It's all fake. I'm telling you.

120
00:09:31,700 --> 00:09:33,180
- How come it's fake? 
 - You know what?

121
00:09:33,180 --> 00:09:35,342
- What? 
 - This is what you call inviting trouble in.

122
00:09:35,342 --> 00:09:37,630
- What are you saying? 
 - It's The Farmer and the Snake!

123
00:09:37,630 --> 00:09:38,870
- Nonsense. 
 - Dad!

124
00:09:38,870 --> 00:09:40,160
- What's wrong? 
 - What are you saying?

125
00:09:40,160 --> 00:09:41,875
- You tell me! 
 - I can't talk to you!

126
00:09:41,875 --> 00:09:43,837
Who said you can go? I haven't finished talking.

127
00:09:43,837 --> 00:09:46,250
What are you doing?

128
00:09:49,420 --> 00:09:54,350
Who said his daughter is grown up, and wants her to live her own life?

129
00:09:54,350 --> 00:09:56,460
Have you forgotten?

130
00:09:56,990 --> 00:10:01,742
I didn't forget, but I won't allow her to have a boyfriend.

131
00:10:03,130 --> 00:10:04,880
Chen Lei.

132
00:10:05,510 --> 00:10:09,720
My daughter has been sensible and obedient since she was little.

133
00:10:09,720 --> 00:10:12,630
Has she ever made you worry?

134
00:10:12,630 --> 00:10:14,208
She's just dating while in college.

135
00:10:14,208 --> 00:10:17,630
And you yelled at her and lectured her in front of others.

136
00:10:17,630 --> 00:10:20,940
Have you thought about her feelings?

137
00:10:20,940 --> 00:10:22,920
How annoying!

138
00:10:31,660 --> 00:10:34,390
It's my first time being a father.

139
00:10:35,230 --> 00:10:38,070
Have any of you considered how I feel?

140
00:11:42,110 --> 00:11:43,630
Dad.

141
00:12:00,350 --> 00:12:02,820
Chen Lei, why are you here so early?

142
00:12:02,820 --> 00:12:04,800
Is Xi Chi at home?

143
00:12:07,270 --> 00:12:10,060
You see, I heard about what happened yesterday.

144
00:12:10,060 --> 00:12:12,270
I lectured him. I don't get it.

145
00:12:12,270 --> 00:12:14,110
Why keep it a secret if you're in a relationship?

146
00:12:14,110 --> 00:12:17,300
Well, Yi Fan. I have something to talk to Xi Chi.

147
00:12:17,300 --> 00:12:19,280
It's okay, Yi Fan.

148
00:12:26,390 --> 00:12:28,180
Uncle Chen.

149
00:12:36,510 --> 00:12:41,510
The way I spoke to you last night was a little rude.

150
00:12:42,060 --> 00:12:44,180
I want to apologize.

151
00:12:46,960 --> 00:12:49,071
Have a seat, let's talk.

152
00:12:56,060 --> 00:12:57,650
 Do you know... 

153
00:12:58,990 --> 00:13:06,040
 that Huan Er was like a poor kitten when she was born? 

154
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:11,580
At that time, I didn't know how to hold her.

155
00:13:12,300 --> 00:13:15,030
Later, Huan Er was in poor health.

156
00:13:15,030 --> 00:13:17,560
Her mom and I were so worried.

157
00:13:17,560 --> 00:13:19,720
We kept accompanying her.

158
00:13:20,660 --> 00:13:26,410
At that time, we both thought that as long as Huan Er could live well,

159
00:13:26,410 --> 00:13:28,580
 nothing else mattered. 

160
00:13:30,150 --> 00:13:36,150
That's why Huan Er and Aunt Li Na...

161
00:13:36,960 --> 00:13:40,460
are the two most important women in my life.

162
00:13:42,650 --> 00:13:45,290
But now?

163
00:13:46,110 --> 00:13:48,300
To put it metaphorically…

164
00:13:48,300 --> 00:13:53,560
You're going to take one of them away from me.

165
00:13:54,410 --> 00:13:59,450
And honestly, that's hard for me to accept.

166
00:14:01,170 --> 00:14:02,930
You may not understand.

167
00:14:02,930 --> 00:14:08,853
Maybe you'll understand when you become a father.

168
00:14:11,170 --> 00:14:13,090
Uncle Chen.

169
00:14:14,700 --> 00:14:19,350
I'm serious about Huan Er.

170
00:14:19,350 --> 00:14:21,920
I swear, I'll never let her down.

171
00:14:22,510 --> 00:14:25,700
It's not that I'm dissatisfied with you.

172
00:14:25,700 --> 00:14:30,560
It's just that I have my own concerns because I've been through this before.

173
00:14:31,750 --> 00:14:36,910
Many promises made by young people may not necessarily be fulfilled.

174
00:14:36,910 --> 00:14:43,030
Very few people end up marrying their first love.

175
00:14:44,800 --> 00:14:48,110
But still... you two are already at this point.

176
00:14:48,110 --> 00:14:52,350
If I tried to stop you now, I'd just seem selfish.

177
00:14:53,200 --> 00:14:58,940
So I'm here today to make a few things clear to you.

178
00:14:58,940 --> 00:15:00,660
Go ahead.

179
00:15:02,910 --> 00:15:04,560
First,

180
00:15:05,440 --> 00:15:10,660
if you two are going to be together, then you have my blessing.

181
00:15:12,560 --> 00:15:16,650
But remember to be nice to Huan Er.

182
00:15:16,650 --> 00:15:18,870
Don't ever hurt her.

183
00:15:21,150 --> 00:15:25,080
Second, If things don't work out between you,

184
00:15:25,080 --> 00:15:29,900
I hope you can still part on good terms, and stay friends.

185
00:15:29,900 --> 00:15:32,708
After all, you two grew up together.

186
00:15:32,708 --> 00:15:35,460
It's not easy to be friends for so many years.

187
00:15:35,460 --> 00:15:39,390
Her mom and I can't be with her forever.

188
00:15:39,390 --> 00:15:43,993
If one day we're no longer around, and Huan Er encounters difficulties,

189
00:15:43,993 --> 00:15:48,870
I hope she has a friend

190
00:15:48,870 --> 00:15:53,070
who knows her well to help her.

191
00:15:56,560 --> 00:15:58,610
Can you promise me that?

192
00:16:01,080 --> 00:16:02,900
Uncle Chen.

193
00:16:03,820 --> 00:16:07,590
I want to be upfront with you, too.

194
00:16:08,270 --> 00:16:12,920
I will take good care of Chen Huan Er.

195
00:16:12,920 --> 00:16:16,000
 She's not just important to you, 

196
00:16:17,630 --> 00:16:20,130
but also the most important person to me.

197
00:16:25,300 --> 00:16:26,850
Okay.

198
00:16:29,150 --> 00:16:32,500
In that case, we have a deal.

199
00:16:47,030 --> 00:16:49,120
- Yi Fan. 
 - Well...

200
00:16:49,120 --> 00:16:52,550
- Don't you want to sit for a while? 
 - No, I'm leaving.

201
00:17:15,964 --> 00:17:17,590
Dad...

202
00:17:41,460 --> 00:17:43,490
You want to go abroad?

203
00:17:47,880 --> 00:17:50,057
I'm thinking about it.

204
00:17:50,057 --> 00:17:52,390
Since I want to study creative writing,

205
00:17:52,390 --> 00:17:54,700
the earlier I start learning English, the better.

206
00:17:55,530 --> 00:17:57,840
But I haven't made any final decisions yet.

207
00:17:59,460 --> 00:18:00,789
Song Cong.

208
00:18:00,789 --> 00:18:05,070
If I go abroad, will you support me?

209
00:18:05,070 --> 00:18:08,500
Studying abroad would definitely help with your writing.

210
00:18:08,500 --> 00:18:10,520
Of course I support you.

211
00:18:12,180 --> 00:18:15,010
Will you consider going abroad?

212
00:18:16,440 --> 00:18:18,420
I have to study for eight years.

213
00:18:18,420 --> 00:18:21,640
At least for now, I'm not planning on it.

214
00:18:21,640 --> 00:18:23,460
What about eight years later?

215
00:18:23,460 --> 00:18:25,460
Eight years later?

216
00:18:27,790 --> 00:18:31,220
I haven't thought about things so far into the future.

217
00:18:31,220 --> 00:18:35,920
I think I need to focus on what I can learn right now.

218
00:18:38,830 --> 00:18:40,590
Are you...

219
00:18:41,830 --> 00:18:46,770
willing to change the trajectory of your life for me?

220
00:18:50,070 --> 00:18:51,800
I...

221
00:18:53,630 --> 00:18:55,790
I'm kidding.

222
00:18:55,790 --> 00:18:58,920
Did you know that my mom made malicious assumptions about you,

223
00:18:58,920 --> 00:19:01,397
saying you'd try to hold me back.

224
00:19:02,700 --> 00:19:03,980
I won't stop you.

225
00:19:03,980 --> 00:19:05,630
Don't worry.

226
00:19:06,220 --> 00:19:10,520
I think... you should stick to your dream.

227
00:19:15,420 --> 00:19:17,450
Honestly,

228
00:19:18,460 --> 00:19:22,180
part of me actually wished you would try to stop me.

229
00:19:23,630 --> 00:19:30,020
Then at least I'd know you want to be in my future.

230
00:19:38,120 --> 00:19:40,700
Song Cong.

231
00:19:40,700 --> 00:19:45,690
Why don't we... break up?

232
00:19:50,830 --> 00:19:56,530
Actually, I've known for a long time that we're not from the same world.

233
00:19:57,260 --> 00:20:02,220
We love freedom, but what we want from it is different.

234
00:20:02,970 --> 00:20:05,070
All these years,

235
00:20:05,700 --> 00:20:11,170
I changed a lot for us to be together.

236
00:20:12,460 --> 00:20:17,830
I even became less and less like myself.

237
00:20:24,870 --> 00:20:26,650
Qi Qi.

238
00:20:27,660 --> 00:20:32,140
Actually, you were already incredible.

239
00:20:32,810 --> 00:20:35,942
You never needed to change for me.

240
00:20:37,640 --> 00:20:39,255
No.

241
00:20:39,255 --> 00:20:41,120
You don't understand.

242
00:20:45,000 --> 00:20:50,700
Back in high school, you shone so brightly.

243
00:20:51,310 --> 00:20:54,500
So brightly, it made me feel like I didn't deserve you.

244
00:20:55,020 --> 00:21:00,010
All I could do was stand behind you and watch your back.

245
00:21:05,740 --> 00:21:10,010
All this time, I've been chasing after you.

246
00:21:13,150 --> 00:21:15,120
I'm tired.

247
00:21:23,070 --> 00:21:27,140
I understand what you're saying.

248
00:21:28,070 --> 00:21:29,890
Because...

249
00:21:31,600 --> 00:21:34,899
right now, I'm chasing after you, too.

250
00:21:37,450 --> 00:21:39,760
In your world,

251
00:21:40,550 --> 00:21:45,240
I might just be an ordinary university student.

252
00:21:45,240 --> 00:21:50,080
Compared with your imaginative and exciting life,

253
00:21:51,920 --> 00:21:54,410
my life is plain.

254
00:21:59,120 --> 00:22:04,730
Maybe our lives were meant to be two lines that only cross once,

255
00:22:06,220 --> 00:22:09,490
meeting at one fixed moment in time.

256
00:22:24,220 --> 00:22:26,320
Can we hug?

257
00:23:25,550 --> 00:23:27,630
 Mom. 

258
00:23:27,630 --> 00:23:33,560
 All these years, you've used love as a reason to pressure me into doing what you want. 

259
00:23:34,070 --> 00:23:38,320
