 Hello. I'm Qi Qi. Huan Er is my desk mate. 

281
00:25:02,020 --> 00:25:03,500
 Hello. 

282
00:25:04,780 --> 00:25:06,660
♫  All right  ♫

283
00:25:06,660 --> 00:25:10,600
♫  Let's not meet again  ♫

284
00:25:12,060 --> 00:25:19,300
♫  I want you to remember me  ♫

285
00:25:31,790 --> 00:25:35,390
 Our university life just kept going on. 

286
00:25:37,600 --> 00:25:40,265
Are you planning to apply for a postgraduate?

287
00:25:40,265 --> 00:25:42,740
I need to prepare early.

288
00:25:42,740 --> 00:25:44,500
Is it stressful?

289
00:25:45,630 --> 00:25:48,110
It's definitely stressful.

290
00:25:48,110 --> 00:25:49,500
But I'll just keep calm.

291
00:25:49,500 --> 00:25:52,700
Even if I don't pass, I can always try again.

292
00:25:52,700 --> 00:25:54,840
You'll be fine.

293
00:25:56,210 --> 00:25:58,150
Huan Er.

294
00:25:58,150 --> 00:26:00,560
I'm going to Huan Dao Technology tomorrow.

295
00:26:00,560 --> 00:26:03,420
I talked to them about a new collaboration model.

296
00:26:03,420 --> 00:26:05,880
They'd basically invest in me,

297
00:26:05,880 --> 00:26:10,020
and I'd officially join the team. They'd help me expand the workforce.

298
00:26:10,020 --> 00:26:11,500
Isn't that good?

299
00:26:11,500 --> 00:26:14,308
It's indeed good. It's just that...

300
00:26:14,308 --> 00:26:16,660
Right now, it's just me and Zhou Ye handling everything.

301
00:26:16,660 --> 00:26:22,970
I'm just worried that if things get busy, I won't have much time for you.

302
00:26:23,700 --> 00:26:25,010
No way.

303
00:26:25,010 --> 00:26:27,740
When did you become so clingy?

304
00:26:27,740 --> 00:26:30,830
I've always been kind of clingy, actually.

305
00:26:30,830 --> 00:26:32,560
Really?

306
00:26:33,630 --> 00:26:35,960
- I'll get water. 
 - Wait.

307
00:26:35,960 --> 00:26:38,760
I'll go. Sit.

308
00:26:39,500 --> 00:26:40,630
Phone.

309
00:26:40,630 --> 00:26:42,397
Why did you take your phone?

310
00:26:42,397 --> 00:26:45,275
- Don't bother. 
 - Are you hiding something from me?

311
00:26:51,020 --> 00:26:53,080
Why isn't he here yet?

312
00:26:59,460 --> 00:27:00,630
Xi Chi.

313
00:27:00,630 --> 00:27:02,420
Thanks.

314
