 - No.

317
00:27:09,120 --> 00:27:10,660
The price will go up when you get back.

318
00:27:10,660 --> 00:27:11,830
How much?

319
00:27:11,830 --> 00:27:13,520
200.

320
00:27:13,520 --> 00:27:15,780
Zhou Ye, do you have any heart?

321
00:27:17,120 --> 00:27:20,158
Call me if you need me for something like this again.

322
00:27:25,210 --> 00:27:28,730
Here. Water, and this.

323
00:27:30,986 --> 00:27:32,010
Did you buy this for me?

324
00:27:32,010 --> 00:27:33,870
Of course.

325
00:27:38,390 --> 00:27:40,297
Why is it brown sugar ginger tea?

326
00:27:40,297 --> 00:27:42,142
What do you think?

327
00:27:44,150 --> 00:27:45,630
How do you know it's today?

328
00:27:45,630 --> 00:27:47,360
How could I not know?

329
00:27:47,360 --> 00:27:50,770
Aunt Li Na has always reminded you not to drink cold drinks during your period.

330
00:27:50,770 --> 00:27:52,970
Even I remember, but you don't.

331
00:27:52,970 --> 00:27:55,010
I wondered how my mom knew my every move.

332
00:27:55,010 --> 00:27:57,320
So it was you all along. You sneaky spy.

333
00:27:57,320 --> 00:28:00,040
As long as it's good for your health, I can be a spy.

334
00:28:00,040 --> 00:28:02,220
- Drink it while it's hot. 
 - No.

335
00:28:02,220 --> 00:28:06,220
It tastes like ginger. I don't want to drink it. I don't like it.

336
00:28:06,220 --> 00:28:08,550
- Hurry. 
 - You...

337
00:28:12,730 --> 00:28:14,520
Done.

338
00:28:16,080 --> 00:28:17,350
No.

339
00:28:17,350 --> 00:28:18,500
Library.

340
00:28:18,500 --> 00:28:20,630
It's a library.

341
00:28:23,080 --> 00:28:25,040
Finish this.

342
00:28:39,150 --> 00:28:41,110
I'm tired.

343
00:28:43,180 --> 00:28:44,740
Chen Huan Er, don't be lazy.

344
00:28:44,740 --> 00:28:45,980
I'm tired.

345
00:28:45,980 --> 00:28:48,350
Lend me your shoulder.

346
00:28:49,500 --> 00:28:52,231
You get five minutes. That's it.

347
00:29:10,380 --> 00:29:12,660
   

348
00:29:12,660 --> 00:29:14,830
- Hello? Mom. 
  - Cong. 

349
00:29:14,830 --> 00:29:18,700
 I had your dad send you 500 more yuan for this month's expenses. 

350
00:29:18,700 --> 00:29:21,390
 Don't just stay in your dorm and study all weekend. 

351
00:29:21,390 --> 00:29:23,830
Take Qi Qi out for a meal or something.

352
00:29:23,830 --> 00:29:26,640
 No need, Mom. I don't spend that much. 

353
00:29:26,640 --> 00:29:28,830
You don't need to transfer so much to me in the future.

354
00:29:28,830 --> 00:29:30,260
 It's not for you. 

355
00:29:30,260 --> 00:29:32,760
 It's to let you spend on Qi Qi. 

356
00:29:34,980 --> 00:29:38,250
We actually broke up a while ago.

357
00:29:40,390 --> 00:29:42,310
What happened?

358
00:29:42,310 --> 00:29:44,310
Why did you break up?

359
00:29:46,110 --> 00:29:47,700
Mom, my roommate is back.

360
00:29:47,700 --> 00:29:50,080
I'll talk to you later.

361
00:30:04,320 --> 00:30:06,876
How did your internship interview go?

362
00:30:07,640 --> 00:30:09,075
I switched majors halfway through.

363
00:30:09,075 --> 00:30:11,520
It's not that easy to find a job.

364
00:30:11,520 --> 00:30:14,560
Have you decided to switch from clinical to pharmaceuticals?

365
00:30:14,560 --> 00:30:16,260
I've thought it through.

366
00:30:16,260 --> 00:30:18,770
Clinical medicine takes too much time.

367
00:30:18,770 --> 00:30:22,180
In one year, all the four-year students will be able to work and earn money.

368
00:30:22,180 --> 00:30:24,310
Yet we still have to go to class.

369
00:30:24,310 --> 00:30:27,475
Even if I can work in a good hospital, the salary won't be high.

370
00:30:27,475 --> 00:30:30,550
The effort just doesn't match the reward.

371
00:30:30,550 --> 00:30:32,720
Besides, I come from an average family.

372
00:30:32,720 --> 00:30:36,730
I feel guilty asking my parents for money in my twenties.

373
00:30:44,280 --> 00:30:47,140
Could you please share the WeChat of the group admin for the part-time job group

374
00:30:47,140 --> 00:30:48,390
you mentioned last time?

375
00:30:48,390 --> 00:30:50,180
Sure.

376
00:30:52,980 --> 00:30:55,046
- I've sent it. 
 - Okay.

377
00:31:02,420 --> 00:31:04,770
- Jing. 
 - Mr. Jiang.

378
00:31:04,770 --> 00:31:06,460
- You're here. 
 - Long time no see.

379
00:31:06,460 --> 00:31:08,510
Welcome.

380
00:31:08,510 --> 00:31:11,140
This is Zhou Ye from my team.

381
00:31:11,140 --> 00:31:12,964
- Hello. 
 - Hello, Zhou Ye.

382
00:31:12,964 --> 00:31:15,197
- I'm Jiang Sen. 
 - Hello, Mr. Jiang.

383
00:31:15,197 --> 00:31:17,150
We can finally cooperate officially.

384
00:31:17,150 --> 00:31:19,564
We're looking forward to working with Huan Dao too.

385
00:31:19,564 --> 00:31:21,310
Me too.

386
00:31:22,180 --> 00:31:23,260
Mr. Jiang.

387
00:31:23,260 --> 00:31:24,260
You're here.

388
00:31:24,260 --> 00:31:27,960
- Fu Ying. 
 - Fu Ying, do you work here?

389
00:31:27,960 --> 00:31:31,020
We have Ms. Fu to thank for introducing us.

390
00:31:31,020 --> 00:31:33,840
Jing, your project is good. And Mr. Jiang has a keen eye for talent.

391
00:31:33,840 --> 00:31:35,629
I just made the introduction.

392
00:31:35,629 --> 00:31:38,631
- Thank you, Fu Ying. 
 - Thank you.

393
00:31:38,631 --> 00:31:39,700
All right, don't mention it.

394
00:31:39,700 --> 00:31:41,600
Fu Ying, show them around.

395
00:31:41,600 --> 00:31:43,650
- I have a meeting to attend. I'll go to work. 
 - Okay.

396
00:31:43,650 --> 00:31:45,600
Okay, Mr. Jiang.

397
00:31:47,240 --> 00:31:48,611
Thank you, Fu Ying.

398
00:31:48,611 --> 00:31:49,940
Fu Ying, are you free someday?

399
00:31:49,940 --> 00:31:52,220
We'll treat you to a meal.

400
00:31:52,220 --> 00:31:55,080
I'd love to, but I have a business trip tomorrow.

401
00:31:55,080 --> 00:31:56,560
How about we do it tonight?

402
00:31:56,560 --> 00:31:57,971
We can do it tonight.

403
00:31:57,971 --> 00:32:00,886
But my girlfriend's coming to see me. Do you mind if she joins us?

404
00:32:00,886 --> 00:32:02,480
The more, the merrier. I don't mind.

405
00:32:02,480 --> 00:32:04,880
I'll go upstairs and deliver a document first. Sit here and wait for me.

406
00:32:04,880 --> 00:32:06,360
Sure.

407
00:32:09,000 --> 00:32:12,078
- Jing Xi Chi, have you lost your mind? 
 - What's wrong?

408
00:32:12,078 --> 00:32:14,350
You're taking your rumored girlfriend to dinner with your current girlfriend.

409
00:32:14,350 --> 00:32:16,550
- Huan Er will be jealous! 
 - What rumored girlfriend?

410
00:32:16,550 --> 00:32:17,790
Hui Xin told me everything.

411
00:32:17,790 --> 00:32:19,630
You and Fu Ying were photographed in the library.

412
00:32:19,630 --> 00:32:22,630
- It's already all over the place. I know! 
 - What is this all about?

413
00:32:22,630 --> 00:32:25,630
Fu Ying and I had nothing going on. We're innocent.

414
00:32:25,630 --> 00:32:28,600
Besides, Huan Er isn't like that. She won't believe it.

415
00:32:28,600 --> 00:32:31,697
It doesn't matter. You should avoid suspicion in such matters.

416
00:32:31,697 --> 00:32:34,200
Rumors spread like wildfire. Do you understand?

417
00:32:34,200 --> 00:32:36,070
You have too little experience in dating.

418
00:32:36,070 --> 00:32:39,142
Girls are usually pretty sensitive about this stuff.

419
00:32:39,940 --> 00:32:41,840
Is it that serious?

420
00:32:41,840 --> 00:32:45,350
If you don't believe what I say, you can witness it yourself tonight.

421
00:32:45,350 --> 00:32:47,040
I... I'm telling you.

422
00:32:47,040 --> 00:32:48,604
I'm not joining this dinner. I have something to do.

423
00:32:48,604 --> 00:32:50,520
Are you my buddy? Why are you not coming?

424
00:32:50,520 --> 00:32:53,350
- I... 
 - Let's go. I'll show you around.

425
00:32:53,350 --> 00:32:55,497
- Okay. 
 - Come on. This way.

426
00:32:56,310 --> 00:32:57,550
Think it over.

427
00:32:57,550 --> 00:32:58,708
What do you have to do?

428
00:32:58,708 --> 00:33:00,608
I'm not going no matter what.

429
00:33:04,700 --> 00:33:06,680
Sorry. Am I late?

430
00:33:06,680 --> 00:33:09,500
Huan Er, right? See what's there to eat.

431
00:33:09,500 --> 00:33:10,500
I'm okay with anything.

432
00:33:10,500 --> 00:33:12,840
- I'll order then. 
 - Okay.

433
00:33:12,840 --> 00:33:14,260
Are you tired?

434
00:33:14,260 --> 00:33:15,942
- A little. 
 - Here. Drink some water.

435
00:33:15,942 --> 00:33:16,980
We'll order these first.

436
00:33:16,980 --> 00:33:19,120
- Thank you. 
 - Drink some.

437
00:33:21,520 --> 00:33:24,220
How was it? It's a long way here, right?

438
00:33:24,220 --> 00:33:27,160
Indeed. It takes about an hour and a half by bus.

439
00:33:27,160 --> 00:33:31,040
Yes. Huan Dao Technology is a bit far from our school.

440
00:33:31,040 --> 00:33:33,200
Have you considered renting a place?

441
00:33:33,200 --> 00:33:34,932
I've been looking for a place lately.

442
00:33:34,932 --> 00:33:36,680
Why don't you check out my residential area?

443
00:33:36,680 --> 00:33:40,160
It's very close to the company. It's only a ten-minute walk.

444
00:33:40,160 --> 00:33:43,453
The key is that it's an old residential area. The rent is affordable.

445
00:33:45,280 --> 00:33:47,870
- Isn't it a good idea? 
 - Yes.

446
00:33:47,870 --> 00:33:52,630
Fu Ying, if it's convenient, could you give me the agent's contact information?

447
00:33:52,630 --> 00:33:54,875
No problem. Let's add each other on WeChat first.

448
00:33:54,875 --> 00:33:56,408
Sure. Thank you.

449
00:33:57,500 --> 00:33:59,110
Thank you.

450
00:34:05,830 --> 00:34:07,070
Fu Ying.

451
00:34:07,070 --> 00:34:09,060
I want to ask you a question.

452
00:34:09,060 --> 00:34:10,650
Go ahead.

453
00:34:11,270 --> 00:34:14,540
What lipstick shade are you wearing?

454
00:34:15,540 --> 00:34:18,670
I thought you wanted to ask me why I became a programmer?

455
00:34:18,670 --> 00:34:20,790
Why would I ask you that?

456
00:34:20,790 --> 00:34:23,910
Girls can do whatever job they want.

457
00:34:23,910 --> 00:34:25,670
You're right, Huan Er.

458
00:34:25,670 --> 00:34:28,140
I used to hate it when people asked me this question.

459
00:34:28,140 --> 00:34:30,140
You're the only one who didn't ask me that.

460
00:34:30,140 --> 00:34:32,578
Fu Ying, people always ask me questions too.

461
00:34:32,578 --> 00:34:36,831
They asked me why I applied for Sports Department, and why did I learn martial arts.

462
00:34:36,831 --> 00:34:39,460
Why are there so many questions? Learning martial arts is great.

463
00:34:39,460 --> 00:34:41,650
I can carry two buckets up five floors

464
00:34:41,650 --> 00:34:43,200
without breaking a sweat.

465
00:34:43,200 --> 00:34:44,690
Amazing.

466
00:34:44,690 --> 00:34:47,080
After hearing you say that, I think I need to train too.

467
00:34:47,080 --> 00:34:49,073
Or I'll get occupational diseases by sitting all day long.

468
00:34:49,073 --> 00:34:51,500
You can try out Baduanjin.

469
00:34:51,500 --> 00:34:53,060
- Baduanjin? 
 - Yes.

470
00:34:53,060 --> 00:34:58,020
You can keep fit by practicing, for a few minutes every day. It's easy.

471
00:34:58,020 --> 00:35:00,160
 How come it's different from what Zhou Ye said? 

472
00:35:00,160 --> 00:35:02,142
Didn't I tell you to try it before? Did you even try it?

473
00:35:02,142 --> 00:35:03,840
I did. It's good.

474
00:35:03,840 --> 00:35:06,300
