475
00:35:06,300 --> 00:35:08,750
- Do you have any... 
 - It's fine. I can send you the video.

476
00:35:08,750 --> 00:35:10,460
Okay.

477
00:35:16,100 --> 00:35:17,940
Why are you smiling?

478
00:35:17,940 --> 00:35:20,540
I'm laughing at Zhou Ye's nonsense.

479
00:35:20,540 --> 00:35:21,790
What did he say?

480
00:35:21,790 --> 00:35:25,390
He said you'd be upset about me working with Fu Ying.

481
00:35:26,060 --> 00:35:29,060
How do you know I don't mind?

482
00:35:29,060 --> 00:35:32,540
What, did you expect me to sit here glaring at her all night?

483
00:35:32,540 --> 00:35:34,340
No.

484
00:35:35,640 --> 00:35:36,540
Jing Xi Chi.

485
00:35:36,540 --> 00:35:40,790
Are you happy to be able to work with a beautiful senior?

486
00:35:40,790 --> 00:35:42,120
How could I be happy?

487
00:35:42,120 --> 00:35:45,190
I'm telling you. Fu Ying is scary at work. She often scolds people.

488
00:35:45,190 --> 00:35:48,500
I don't think so. Didn't she help you find a house? She's also nice to you.

489
00:35:48,500 --> 00:35:52,310
No, no, she's just being helpful. That's all.

490
00:35:52,310 --> 00:35:54,390
Helpful?

491
00:35:55,540 --> 00:35:57,070
Helpful...

492
00:35:58,350 --> 00:36:01,390
Don't be like this. You're scaring me.

493
00:36:01,390 --> 00:36:02,910
You're scared?

494
00:36:02,910 --> 00:36:05,060
- You're scared now? 
 - Yes.

495
00:36:05,060 --> 00:36:08,180
You'd better behave and listen.

496
00:36:08,910 --> 00:36:10,350
Don't worry.

497
00:36:10,350 --> 00:36:11,790
Heaven can bear witness.

498
00:36:11,790 --> 00:36:18,330
I... I swear on this streetlamp I'll do whatever you say.

499
00:36:20,453 --> 00:36:22,370
You don't believe me?

500
00:36:26,400 --> 00:36:28,127
Do you believe me now?

501
00:36:29,100 --> 00:36:30,980
What are you doing?

502
00:36:31,830 --> 00:36:33,790
What's wrong?

503
00:36:33,790 --> 00:36:36,640
- I... 
 - What's wrong?

504
00:36:36,640 --> 00:36:37,540
I believe.

505
00:36:37,540 --> 00:36:39,610
Isn't it normal for a young couple to kiss?

506
00:36:39,610 --> 00:36:41,467
What's wrong with that?

507
00:36:50,480 --> 00:36:52,844
I didn't expect it to be you.

508
00:36:55,760 --> 00:36:57,320
I didn't expect it to be you either.

509
00:36:57,320 --> 00:36:59,980
I started working part-time when I was a freshman.

510
00:36:59,980 --> 00:37:01,940
But I kept getting scammed by agents.

511
00:37:01,940 --> 00:37:04,500
In a rage, I created this group myself,

512
00:37:04,500 --> 00:37:07,880
thinking I could help students find a reliable job.

513
00:37:07,880 --> 00:37:09,670
You don't have to worry about commissions.

514
00:37:09,670 --> 00:37:12,520
My fees are paid by the clients.

515
00:37:12,520 --> 00:37:15,710
I heard from my roommate that your group is well-managed.

516
00:37:15,710 --> 00:37:17,110
Thank you.

517
00:37:18,460 --> 00:37:21,200
Can I ask why you want to work part-time?

518
00:37:21,200 --> 00:37:24,120
I just want to save some money before graduation.

519
00:37:24,620 --> 00:37:26,220
Got it.

520
00:37:27,080 --> 00:37:29,850
I have a job suitable for you.

521
00:37:29,850 --> 00:37:31,670
The client's kid is in the first year of high school.

522
00:37:31,670 --> 00:37:35,230
