528
00:38:02,060 --> 00:38:04,100
Sit here. There's no place now.

529
00:38:04,100 --> 00:38:05,910
What about you?

530
00:38:05,910 --> 00:38:07,910
I happen to start my shift.

531
00:38:07,910 --> 00:38:09,940
- Shift? 
 - I found a part-time job.

532
00:38:09,940 --> 00:38:11,870
I have to work three half-days a week.

533
00:38:11,870 --> 00:38:13,670
With all the academic pressure,

534
00:38:13,670 --> 00:38:16,120
you're still working part-time three half-days a week?

535
00:38:16,120 --> 00:38:19,489
University isn't like high school. Don't just study.

536
00:38:19,489 --> 00:38:21,408
I consider it an internship. I'll get paid too.

537
00:38:21,408 --> 00:38:22,942
Bye.

538
00:38:32,020 --> 00:38:35,075
You can read. I'll stop bothering you.

539
00:38:55,870 --> 00:38:57,340
Come in.

540
00:38:59,460 --> 00:39:02,390
Hello. I'm here to see Professor...

541
00:39:13,140 --> 00:39:15,060
It's you.

542
00:39:15,060 --> 00:39:18,931
Professor Qiu said a junior would be here to deliver documents.

543
00:39:18,931 --> 00:39:21,080
I didn't expect it to be you.

544
00:39:21,080 --> 00:39:22,500
He went out for something.

545
00:39:22,500 --> 00:39:25,108
Give me the documents. I'll take them to his office for you.

546
00:39:25,108 --> 00:39:27,660
Sure. Thank you.

547
00:39:29,440 --> 00:39:32,830
Do you also want to pursue a graduate program under Professor Qiu?

548
