Are you already Professor Qiu's graduate student?

549
00:39:37,750 --> 00:39:41,920
Yes. I just got admitted to Professor Qiu's graduate program.

550
00:39:45,940 --> 00:39:47,980
I can see that you're busy.

551
00:39:47,980 --> 00:39:49,540
I got to go.

552
00:39:49,540 --> 00:39:51,080
Sure.

553
00:40:17,720 --> 00:40:19,987
It looks much more comfortable now.

554
00:40:23,840 --> 00:40:26,086
The chores looked like a lot, but they're quite easy to manage.

555
00:40:26,086 --> 00:40:28,220
I finished at nine o'clock.

556
00:40:29,670 --> 00:40:31,390
Really?

