It's out of batteries.

568
00:41:15,060 --> 00:41:19,390
Well... What do we do now?

569
00:41:20,790 --> 00:41:23,100
What can we do?

570
00:41:23,100 --> 00:41:26,820
If you can't go back, stay here.

